<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Figo" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Figo</orth> (cf. <emph>Fico</emph>), fig, a contemptible trifle: <cit><quote>f. for thy friendship,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.60" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 60</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the f. for thee,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 60</bibl></cit> (== I do not care for thee).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>